          <h2>API v1</h2>
          <h3>Search Yasb</h3>
<p>Search an IP:</p>
<pre><code class="bash">curl http://yasb.intuxication.org/api/check.xml?ip=&lt;IPv4&gt;
</code></pre>
<p>Response:</p>
<pre><code class="xml">&lt;result&gt;
    &lt;ip&gt;IPv4&lt;/ip&gt;
    &lt;spam&gt;Boolean&lt;spam&gt;
&lt;/result&gt;
</code></pre>
<p>Submit an IP:</p>
<pre><code class="bash">curl http://yasb.intuxication.org/api/submit.xml?ip=&lt;IPv4&gt;
</code></pre>
<p>Response:</p>
<pre><code class="xml">&lt;result&gt;
    &lt;ip&gt;IPv4&lt;/ip&gt;
    &lt;spam&gt;Boolean&lt;spam&gt;
&lt;/result&gt;
</code></pre>
        </div>
