          <h2>News</h2>
          <h4>2014/08/23 : Code available</h4>
          <p>Yasb is now opensource at <a href="http://github.com/bjorand/yasb">github</a>.</p>
          <h4>2009/03/07 : Better accuracy</h4>
          <p>Yasb now features blacklists from spamhaus, spamcop and
            projecthoneypot. All queries done with api/check.xml are now checked
            against those blacklists and yasb internal database is updated.
          </p>
          <h4>2008/01/05 : Launch of Yasb !</h4>
          <p>Yasb is a spam blocker service which lists IP of web spamners.
            It can be interfaced with wiki, forums or blogs software. An API is
            provided to query Yasb database in order to check IPs and report
            new annoying IP.
          </p>
